<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='es'>
<head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Nueva Factura Subida</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&display=swap');
      
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #F4F7FE;
        font-family: 'DM Sans', 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        color: #1B2559;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        background-color: #F4F7FE;
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #FFFFFF;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(112, 144, 176, 0.12);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #FFFFFF;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 30px 30px;
      }
      .header img {
        max-width: 180px;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1B2559;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 40px;
        color: #1B2559;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #1B2559;
      }
      .details-card {
        background-color: #F4F7FE;
        padding: 24px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        margin: 30px 0;
      }
      .details-card ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .details-card li {
        margin: 12px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #1B2559;
      }
      .details-card strong {
        color: #4318FF;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #A3AED0;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        background-color: #F4F7FE;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(163, 174, 208, 0.2);
      }
      .footer p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        color: #A3AED0;
      }
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-wrapper {
          padding: 20px 10px;
        }
        .container {
          border-radius: 16px;
        }
        .content {
          padding: 24px 20px;
        }
        .header {
          padding: 30px 20px 20px;
        }
        .header img {
          max-width: 140px;
        }
        .header h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
          font-size: 14px;
        }
      }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class='email-wrapper'>
        <div class='container'>
            <div class='header'>
                {{#if logoUrl}}
                    <img src='{{logoUrl}}' alt='Viatika Logo' />
                {{/if}}
                <h1>Nueva Factura Subida</h1>
            </div>
            <div class='content'>
                <p>Hola,</p>
                <p>Se ha subido una nueva factura con los siguientes detalles:</p>
                <div class='details-card'>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Proveedor:</strong> {{providerName}}</li>
                        <li><strong>Número de Factura:</strong> {{invoiceNumber}}</li>
                        <li><strong>Fecha:</strong> {{date}}</li>
                        <li><strong>Tipo:</strong> {{type}}</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <p>Por favor, revise la factura y suba el acta de aprobación correspondiente.</p>
            </div>
            <div class='footer'>
                <p>© {{year}} Viatika. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
